l.lognormalizer : module documentation

Part of logsparser

This module exposes the LogNormalizer class that can be used for higher-level management of the normalization flow. Using this module is in no way mandatory in order to benefit from the normalization system; the LogNormalizer class provides basic facilities for further integration in a wider project (web services, ...).
Class LogNormalizer Basic normalization flow manager.
